{"tid":572903,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"習大帝年代：習近平計劃正式稱帝","createTime":"2018-02-26T03:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T03:55:53.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"56358f5378e20b7112f412fbf03a480ef775896b","tid":572903,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:55:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20180225/china-xi-jinping/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fchina%2F20180225%2Fchina-xi-jinping%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=H8NQjG7nlUwDdKTXSy7tVjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=543fed05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20180225/china-xi-jinping/zh-hant/</a><br />\n<br />\n中共提議修憲，取消國家主席任期限制<br />\n<br />\n去年十月，習近平在中共十九大會議上。 <br />\n<br />\n北京&mdash;&mdash;中國共產黨已為國家主席習近平或許無限期地繼續執政掃清了道路。中共本週日宣布，要廢除國家主席任期不超過兩屆的限制。這個令人驚訝的做法，標誌著中國幾十年來最大的政治變化。"}]}